    <item>
      <title>国土安全部削减了与国内极端主义斗争的人员</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-19/dhs-slashes-personnel-leading-fight-against-domestic-extremism</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据现任和前官员的说法，特朗普政府对美国政府工人的清除局势摧毁了一个旨在打击在线激进化的国土安全部门，并认为在过去几年中有助于破坏1000多个暴力地块。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-19/dhs-slashes-personnel-leading-fight-against-domestic-extremism</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 19 Mar 2025 01:21:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普说，与加拿大的自由领导人打交道会更容易</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-19/trump-on-canada-elections-it-ll-be-easier-to-deal-with-liberal-leader</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国总统唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）表示，他宁愿与加拿大的自由党领导人合作，以解决他与渥太华煽动的贸易战，并权衡了邻国北美国家的一次预期民族大选。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-19/trump-on-canada-elections-it-ll-be-easier-to-deal-with-liberal-leader</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 19 Mar 2025 01:12:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>普京在谈话中拒绝乌克兰停火，但特朗普称这是胜利</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-19/putin-spurns-ukraine-ceasefire-in-talks-but-trump-calls-it-a-win</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统弗拉基米尔·普京（Vladimir Putin）拒绝让唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）在乌克兰的30天停火中，他和他的团队要求在结束三年冲突的道路上。对于美国总统来说，这仍然足够好。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-19/putin-spurns-ukraine-ceasefire-in-talks-but-trump-calls-it-a-win</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 19 Mar 2025 01:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普曾经在肯尼迪暗杀中发布归类的文件</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-19/jfk-assassination-records-once-classified-released-by-trump-administration</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）总统周二发布了与前总统约翰·肯尼迪（John F. Kennedy）暗杀有关的先前分类文件，并履行了竞选承诺，以使物质公开。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-19/jfk-assassination-records-once-classified-released-by-trump-administration</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 19 Mar 2025 00:03:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>爱尔兰中央银行修订了对贸易风险的经济预测</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-19/ireland-economy-central-bank-revises-down-forecast-on-trump-trade-war-threat</link>
      <description><![CDATA[爱尔兰中央银行已修改了对经济的看法，理由是地缘政治不确定性的前所未有的增长可能会对爱尔兰产生巨大影响。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-19/ireland-economy-central-bank-revises-down-forecast-on-trump-trade-war-threat</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 19 Mar 2025 00:01:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>扩大英国的“左旋”计划的不平等在于破烂</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-19/inequality-to-widen-as-uk-s-levelling-up-plan-lies-in-tatters</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据新的分析，大多数英国地区将在未来三年内进一步落后于伦敦，这强调了工党政府为改善全国生活水平的挑战。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-19/inequality-to-widen-as-uk-s-levelling-up-plan-lies-in-tatters</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 19 Mar 2025 00:01:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
